rComments: Powerpoints are detailled and explained by prof. Lots of material but exam was good lenght and mix of multiple choice and short answers. BONUS QUESTION so chance of getting 105% on the midterm. He also gives a review sheet and vocabulary to study. Monotone voice but he is a good old man :) I respect him!

Alain Desrochers is an amazing prof! He's always prepared for class and gives a detailed review for midterms and the final that clearly reflect whats on the exam. In general, he's just a great person, so kind and cares about his students. My entire class applauded him at the end of the last lecture. I definitely recommend taking his courses!

Alain Desrochers est un bon professeur. Il est très gentil et sa méthode d'évaluation est très bien pour ceux qui ne sont pas habitués à sont cours. PAR CONTRE, ne prenez pas ce cours si vous n'êtes pas en linguistique ou si vous n'êtes pas porter à étudier beaucoup pour les examens! Ce cours est très demandant!!
He's very passionate about what he teaches but I have never taken a more boring class in my entire life. If you're not studying the french language/grammar, DO NOT take this class.

I had this prof for 3 courses now. He loves want hes doing and is an expert in his field. Some may find his class boring but if you ask questions its pretty interesting. Exams are fair but you have an advantage if your a LIN student. Take time to do your plan and the project will be fine. Overall good prof.
